item.title: Need help with getting my Server ONLINE!
item.dc:creator: @Adobe Adobe
item.description:
@Adobe wrote:

Getting on Skype, not looking for payment as it is against rules.

  1. Offering a reward for someones help is not allowed, help is free on this community.

but also is asking about VPS/online related things.

  1. All topics in this section must be requests for help on a server. Any non-server related questions will be locked. Requesting a host, ‘coder’/programmer, server or client, or asking about a VPS also falls under being non-server related.

but as you left no information about your problem, figured I’d try.

Update- no response, Good luck on the situation
